EDUCATIONAL AND RESEARCH PURPOSE

This software is developed and distributed for educational, research, and
personal experimentation purposes only. HackMate automates the generation of
OpenCore EFI configurations and is intended to assist users in learning about
bootloader configuration, ACPI tables, kernel extensions, and macOS
compatibility on non-Apple hardware.

